room_title: Escape room "Undead Outbreak" by Elite Escape Games in Charleston
room_address: 966 Houston Northcutt Blvd Mt Pleasant, SC 29464
room_description: An outbreak of a devastating virus has ravaged Charleston county, transforming infected humans into brain-eating zombies. The undead horde has surrounded your group in a mysterious research facility filled with valuable supplies and cryptic puzzles. 60 minutes is all the time you have before the herd of infected breach the barricades. Your only chance of survival is team work as you make your way deep into the abandoned laboratory and unlock the secrets hidden within. Your brain is on the menu. Can you use it to escape before time runs out?
